description: The No.1 Currywurst Truck of Orlando is serving up the best German street cuisine in the Sunshine State! Cooked to perfection from the best ingredients around, every delicious dish from this food truck will certainly satisfy your taste buds. For gourmet grub that brings all the best parts of German cooking to you, there's nobody better than The No.1 Currywurst Truck of Orlando!
name: The No.1 Currywurst Truck of Orlando
